    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We determined the antibody response among CoronaVac vaccinees who were boosted with either BNT162b2 or ChAdOx1 nCoV-19. Increase in anti-S-RBD antibodies and surrogate neutralizing antibodies against the Delta variant was higher in BNT162b2 recipients than in ChAdOx1 nCoV-19 recipients. High proportions of reactogenicity were seen for both booster regimens.</jats:p>",
